<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Road Damage API Documentation</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
</head>

<body class="text-blue-500 bg-slate-100 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-10">
        <header class="mb-10">
            <div
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-blue-300 bg-blue-100 px-4 py-1 text-sm text-blue-600 mb-4">
                API Documentation
            </div>

            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">
                Road Damage Classification API
            </h1>

            <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg max-w-3xl">
                REST API untuk klasifikasi kerusakan jalan, melihat model yang tersedia,
                riwayat prediksi, dan menyimpan hasil klasifikasi ke Cloudinary.
            </p>
        </header>

        <section class="mb-10">
            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden p-6 shadow-sm">

                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4" id="info-tabs">
                    <button onclick="showInfoTab('base')"
                        class="info-tab active rounded-xl px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white border border-blue-500 shadow-sm">
                        Base URL
                    </button>
                    <button onclick="showInfoTab('content')"
                        class="info-tab rounded-xl px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 border border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-200">
                        Content Type
                    </button>
                    <button onclick="showInfoTab('upload')"
                        class="info-tab rounded-xl px-4 py-2 bg-slate-100 text-slate-700 border border-slate-300 hover:bg-slate-200">
                        Upload Field
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div id="tab-base" class="tab-content bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6">
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-2">Base URL</p>
                    <code class="text-blue-600 break-all">
                        <a href="<%= BASE_URL %>/api/classification"
                            target="_blank"
                            class="hover:underline">
                                <%= BASE_URL %>/api/classification
                        </a>
                    </code>
                </div>

                <div id="tab-content" class="tab-content hidden bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6">
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-2">Content Type</p>
                    <code class="text-blue-600">multipart/form-data</code>
                </div>

                <div id="tab-upload" class="tab-content hidden bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6">
                    <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-2">Upload Field</p>
                    <code class="text-blue-600">file</code>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <script>
            function showInfoTab(tab) {
                document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content').forEach(el => {
                    el.classList.add('hidden');
                });

                document.querySelectorAll('.info-tab').forEach(el => {
                    el.classList.remove('bg-blue-500', 'text-white', 'border-blue-500');
                    el.classList.add('bg-slate-100', 'text-slate-700', 'border-slate-300');
                });

                document.getElementById(`tab-${tab}`).classList.remove('hidden');

                const activeButton = event.target;
                activeButton.classList.remove('bg-slate-100', 'text-slate-700', 'border-slate-300');
                activeButton.classList.add('bg-blue-500', 'text-white', 'border-blue-500');
            }
        </script>

        <section class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                <div class="border-b border-slate-200 px-6 py-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
                    <span
                        class="bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">GET</span>
                    <code class="text-lg">
                        <a href="<%= BASE_URL %>/api/classification"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
                            /api/classification
                        </a>
                    </code>
                </div>

                <div class="p-6">
                    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">Mengecek status API dan model yang sedang aktif.</p>

                    <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-x-auto">
                        <pre class="text-sm text-slate-700">{
  "status": "ok.",
}</pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                <div class="border-b border-slate-200 px-6 py-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
                    <span
                        class="bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">GET</span>
                    <code class="text-lg">
                        <a href="<%= BASE_URL %>/api/classification/models"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
                            /api/classification/models
                        </a>
                    </code>
                </div>

                <div class="p-6">
                    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">Menampilkan daftar model klasifikasi yang tersedia.</p>

                    <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-x-auto">
                        <pre class="text-sm text-slate-700">{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Berhasil Mendapatkan Model Tersedia",
  "data": {
    "available_models": [
      "Model-RDC-1.1",
      ...
    ]
  }
}</pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                <div class="border-b border-slate-200 px-6 py-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
                    <span
                        class="bg-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">GET</span>
                    <code class="text-lg">
                        <a href="<%= BASE_URL %>/api/classification/history"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
                            /api/classification/history
                        </a>
                    </code>
                </div>

                <div class="p-6">
                    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">Mengambil riwayat hasil klasifikasi yang pernah disimpan.</p>

                    <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-x-auto">
                        <pre class="text-sm text-slate-700">{
  "status": "success",
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "12",
      "image": {
        "url": "https://res.cloudinary.com/...",
        "format": "jpg"
      },
      "model": "Model-RDC-1.1",
      "predictions": [
        {
          "class": "lubang",
          "confidence": 99.96
        },
        {
          "class": "retak",
          "confidence": 0.04
        },
        {
          "class": "alur",
          "confidence": 0
        }
      ] 
},</pre>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                <div class="border-b border-slate-200 px-6 py-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">POST</span>
                    <code class="text-lg">/api/classification/predict</code>
                </div>

                <div class="p-6 space-y-5">
                    <p class="text-slate-700">Upload gambar untuk diprediksi tanpa menyimpan ke database atau
                        Cloudinary.</p>

                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Form Data</p>
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-x-auto">
                            <pre class="text-sm text-slate-700">file: image.jpg</pre>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Contoh Response</p>
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-x-auto">
                            <pre class="text-sm text-slate-700">{
    "status": "success",
    "message": "klasifikasi berhasil!",
    "data": {
        "model": "Model-RDC-1.1",
        "predictions": [
            {
                "class": "lubang",
                "confidence": 99.51
            },
            {
                "class": "retak",
                "confidence": 0.48
            },
            {
                "class": "tidak_rusak",
                "confidence": 0
            }
        ]
    }
}</pre>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                <div class="border-b border-slate-200 px-6 py-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">POST</span>
                    <code class="text-lg">/api/classification/save-predict</code>
                </div>

                <div class="p-6 space-y-5">
                    <p class="text-slate-700">
                        Upload gambar, lakukan prediksi, lalu simpan hasilnya beserta gambar ke Cloudinary.
                    </p>

                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Form Data</p>
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-x-auto">
                            <pre class="text-sm text-slate-700">file: image.jpg</pre>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Contoh Response</p>
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-x-auto">
                            <pre class="text-sm text-slate-700">{
    "status": "success",
    "message": "Data klasifikasi berhasil disimpan",
    "id": "12",
    "data": {
        "image": {
            "url": "https://res.cloudinary.com/...",
            "format": "jpg"
        },
        "model": "mobilenetv2_01",
        "predictions": [
            {
                "class": "lubang",
                "confidence": 100
            },
            {
                "class": "alur",
                "confidence": 0
            },
            {
                "class": "tidak_rusak",
                "confidence": 0
            }
        ],
        "location": {
            "latitude": -2.229,
            "longitude": 113.885,
            "address": "Palangka Raya, ..."
        },
        "created_at": ...,
        "updated_at": ...
    }
}</pre>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                <div class="border-b border-slate-200 px-6 py-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
                    <span class="bg-red-500/20 text-red-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">DELETE</span>
                    <code class="text-lg">/api/classification/:id</code>
                </div>

                <div class="p-6 space-y-5">
                    <p class="text-slate-700">Menghapus data klasifikasi berdasarkan ID.</p>

                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Contoh Request</p>
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-x-auto">
                            <pre class="text-sm text-slate-700">DELETE /api/classification/12</pre>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Contoh Response</p>
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-x-auto">
                            <pre class="text-sm text-slate-700">{
    "status": "success",
    "message": "Data klasifikasi berhasil dihapus",
    "id": "12"
}</pre>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>

</html>